.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
City: boston, nizza, rome, new-york
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to boston and the egyptian##2
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| City         | nizza | boston | new-york | rome  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

