.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
City: london, paris, new-york, miami
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, singing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| City   | london    | paris   | new-york | miami    |
| Hobby      | hiking | drawing | singing       | woodworking |

