2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the tram and the person traveling to paris##2
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the person traveling to rome##2
4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| City    | rome | paris | venice | marseilles |
| Transport   | roller | boat  | train    | tram  |

