3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person traveling to miami is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person traveling to hannover##2
5. the person driving the ship is the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person traveling to hannover##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| City   | new-york | hannover | miami | hamburg     |
| Transport     | airplane | van  | ship   | snowmobile |

