.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, bird, lizard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, scientific, superhero
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the lizard is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Pet         | lizard | bird | rat | turtle   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific | horror      | superhero |

