3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby     | video-games | board-games   | puzzles      | singing      |
| Sport   | skiing     | tennis | basketball | volleyball |

