.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, white, fuchsia, red
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, taxi, tram
1. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
2. the person who likes white is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Color       | brown | fuchsia | red    | white      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

