.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, hiking, woodworking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, alhambra, vegafina, montecristo
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | baking     | chess  | woodworking | hiking |
| Cigar     | dunhill | montecristo | alhambra     | vegafina    |

