.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, tea, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, frog, hamster
1. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
5. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | tea  | almond-milk | juice |
| Pet           | frog     | hamster | bird    | fish     |

