4. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Birthday   | february  | september | december  | april      |
| Job    | musician | bartender | manager | librarian |

