2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
6. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | rock-climbing | dancing | card-games |
| Pet   | hedgehog     | dog       | bird   | chinchilla      |

