3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's sport is badminton and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Sport   | cricket | parkour  | baseball  | badminton |
| Pet           | cat    | hamster | guinea-pig | dog |

