.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, orange, black, mauve
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who likes red##1
7. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Color   | orange     | red     | black          | mauve |
| Sport      | badminton | baseball | weightlifting | sailing  |

 